    80,
    'clytfibo8002mg39qu70p2xwh',
    'BCSB',
    'basalt-columns-sawn-bottom',
    'Basalt Columns Sawn Bottom',
    unistr (
      '<ul><li>Origin: North America</li><li>Classification: Basalt </li><li>Color Range: Blacks, Greys</li><li>Finish: Natural</li><li>Application: Accents</li></ul>\u000d\u000a<p>Basalt Columns are large columnar shape rocks used where vertical landscape features are desired. Monolithic pieces of art, primarily gray in color with some brown or taupe color variations, sawn bottoms make for easy placement and reduced labor costs.\u000d\u000a</p>\u000d\u000a'
