      '<p>Oyster Shell Flour consists of approximately 96% calcium carbonate. The Oyster Shell Flour is sprinkled over the oyster shell, and helps to create a smooth surface once the Oyster Shell Bocce Blend has been applied to the court''s surface.</p>\u000d\u000a'
