    'Quikrete Concrete Mix 80 Lbs',
    unistr (
      '<p>QUIKRETE Concrete Mix (No. 1101) is the original 4000 psi average compressive strength blend of portland cement, sand, and gravel or stone. Just add water. Use for any general concrete work.</p>\u000d\u000a<p>Use for Setting Posts and Building:</p>\u000d\u000a<ul><li>Sidewalks</li><li>Floors</li><li>Steps</li><li>Patios</li><li>Curbs</li><li>Downspout Troughs</li></ul>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a'
