    'Quikrete High Performance Blacktop Repair 50 Lbs',
    unistr (
      '<p>QUIKRETE High Performance Blacktop Repair (No. 1701-52, -62) is a specifically formulated high performance asphalt cold patch material for repairing potholes and cracks over 1" (25.4 mm) wide in asphalt pavements. It is suitable for use on roads, driveways, parking lots, and walkways. All-season formulation is suitable for making permanent repairs in wet or dry conditions.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a'
