VALUES
  (
    24,
    'Bocce Ball Court Materials',
    '<h1>Bocce Court Surface Materials</h1>rnrnWhen building a backyard bocce court, be sure to choose lasting materials that are low maintenance and that facilitate fast play while offering minimal bounce. Choose from our bocce court materials below, or see our guide to building a backyard bocce court for more tips and advice.',
