      '<p>3/8" Crushed Yosemite Tan is decorative gravel that is used in pathways and walkways. The material will contain fines.</p>\u000d\u000a<p>We sell the 3/8" Crushed Yosemite Tan in one cubic foot bag, we supply the bags and you fill them. For larger areas, you''ll want to purchase by the ton. We can load your truck or for a fee, you can use our rental truck or have us deliver to you. For orders over 20 tons please call us for direct pricing.</p><p>3/8" Crushed Yosemite Tan may qualify for LEED Local/Regional Materials credit. Distances vary for each project location. Please verify the materials accordingly.</p>\u000d\u000a'
