    '#1/20 Lapis Lustre Sand 100 Lbs ',
    unistr (
      '<p>CEMEX Lapis Lustre Specialty Sands provide customized blends for uses such as well packing, sandblasting, artificial turf installment, and sports fields. </p> \u000d\u000a<p>CEMEX Lapis Lustre Sands are top quality products that are washed, graded, dried, and certain products are packaged to ensure quality and are tested to be compliant with California ARB Certification standards and NSF 61 Standards. Lapis Lustre Sands are preferred over other manufactured sands due to low dust content and eco-friendly attributes.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p>Coarse/Medium Aquarium: NO #1/20</p>\u000d\u000a<p>Aquarium, Custom Work: Epoxy Mixes, Sandblasting, All Purpose</p>\u000d\u000a'
    ),
    'products',
    127
  );

